3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper deals with privacy-preserving machine learning methods and proposes a novel adaptation network to reduce the influence of image encryption. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image encryption and data augmentation, which are related to multimedia processing. 
5. cs.CY (Computers and Society) - The paper deals with privacy-preserving methods, which have implications for society and privacy concerns.
